author: Lauren Day, Naomi Selvaratnam, Sean Nicholls And Sashka Koloff
title: Think you might have coronavirus? This is what to expect at a testing clinic
description: Four Corners goes inside a COVID-19 screening clinic to see what frontline staff and patients are experiencing every day during the crisis.
